<p>So it ends with Bammargera gaining 6k points for his efforts and a month free on MUD2; Vulnax with 2 weeks free play and 3k points, Legolas and Archangel 1 free week play, and Yuri with 1000 points. </p>
<p>So, do you think it's worth it? Come on and show us what you are made of!</p>
<p>Vulnax reporting ... Signing off, goodnight!</p>
